room_title: Escape room "The Escape Pod" by Wichita Room Escape in Wichita
room_description:
It was a calm and peaceful day out in Deep Space when you hear a loud smash, quickly followed by the WRE ENTERPRISE shaking! You then hear your captain speaking rapidly over the intercom...
"This is your captain speaking! Please enter your respective escape pod as quickly as possible. The WRE ENTERPRISE has been breached!"
Startled and alarmed, you try to gather your crew and get to your escape pod, but it looks like you're about to face some major complications on your way there! Be careful and quick, you have one hour!
